1) Make the first page a “Smart IOC Intake” (like you described)

Paste anything (email text, headers, URL, hash, random blob), then:

auto-extract IOCs (IPs/domains/urls/hashes)
show counts + dedupe
run lookups by type in parallel
return one unified verdict card: “Likely VPN”, “Tor exit”, “Residential”, “Known scanner”, “Malware URL”, etc.
This turns your IOC Extractor into a workflow starter instead of a separate tool.

